** OCCULT1.BBS **

--June 1, 1988.
This is a list of all known public computer bulletin boards
having occult, metaphysical, or religious (non-Christian)
interests. This list may be freely copied and distributed,
provided that it is not altered.

Many of the boards on this list were recently verified to be
in operation. Please let me know if any boards are no longer
running, or if any were deleted in error. This list will
be revised regularly. Please send updates via modem to:

Phil Hansford
Mysteria
(818) 353-8891 (modem only).

The next release of this list is planned for August 1, 1988.

abbreviations --
  P = Paranet
  F = Fidonet Magick Conference (other Fidos not marked)
  R = religion
  $ = charges a fee (ahead of name)
  - = reachable via PC Pursuit (before phone number)

All boards listed operate 24 hours, 300 and 1200 baud unless
otherwise noted.

